reviews: Does what it says and does it well .. all three ports.
Got mine on time. Its a perfect fit (L) and comfortable all over. Material is good quality, does not hang or crease easily. Had a logo screen printed and it took it quite well. Would buy again.

review_title: Does what it is intended for
reviews: Solid build and sturdy. I use it for both Fall and Winter jackets, both youth and adults and it performs well with holding the weight. Would certainly recommend.
Solid product. Strong and stable. I use it for my OSMO 3 device. Would definitely recommend.

review_title: Great SIM card and data package for travelling within Europe
reviews: Received it promptly. Registration was simple and took less than 5 mins. Registered the card three days before travelling. Popped it into my cell phone on the flight before landing. Worked flawlessly in London, Amsterdam, Berlin, Zurich, Rome and Lisbon. Would highly recommend and would definitely use again.

Excellent headset for the price. The only one issue is that the controls are on the rear side of the right speaker, which accidentally get pressed bu the collar bone when set is off triggering the radio.
Worked right out of the box. Nothing to setup or install. Works great!

review_title: Good things comes in small sizes
reviews: Light weight and portable, works as it is advertised. We primarily use it for surfing the net and watching YouTube videos and it works great. Tried with dual display and it works flawlessly. Super quiet.

review_title: Was a handy accessory while it lasted .. short lived.
reviews: The device itself was quite durable, portable and easy to use (plug and play). Just decided one fine day that it'll not work anymore. Luckily I didn't loose much data .. but makes me wonder .. I need to have a backup of my backup!
Been using it for a few month now, works great!

review_title: It OK, just don't expect GoPro quality
reviews: Received as advertised. Its OK as a backup camera, ended up purchasing another cam as my primary capture device. This one just sits as a backup in my bag pack for during those action adventure trips. Video and photo quality are OK.
Exactly as advertised. Connected it with my tablet and a power source, was up an projecting in no time. Plus, their customer service is five stars.
Good quality storage bag for my drone and a couple of backup batteries. I even keep extra propellers in the case.
Good quality product. Magnets are strong and hold decent amount of weight.

Love it! Works as expected. Might help to include in the posting that it's compatible with older GSM frequencies. For Canada use, go with cellular service provided by Petro Canada (Rogers). Bell or Wind is not supported.

review_title: ... works as expected however the shock sensor is of poor quality. Hard bumps to the bike did not ...
reviews: The tilt sensor works as expected however the shock sensor is of poor quality. Hard bumps to the bike did not trigger the alarm, even after trying to set it up at different shock sensitivity levels. Its either a faulty device or a poor quality build since the previous one I had worked fine. Also one of the two remotes was malfunctioning right out of the box - confirmed it with their support as well. Will have to send it in the mail to get a replacement.
